small wound on back (possibly a cookie cutter shark wound).
Partially healed

Hooked by large hook with thick trace/line attached.  Appears to have ingested or be hooked through gills.  Gear thought to be from commercial fishing, assumed from a shark fishery further south (likely NSW).
